    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can touch a dying creature and channel its life energy into another living creature. This ability acts as @Compendium[pf1.spells.k0k8gvqyy3rd5gke]{Death Knell}, except you can choose any ally (including yourself ) within 30 feet to gain the benefit of this effect, and you can apply the +2 enhancement bonus to either Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your Charisma modifier.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 5th level to select this revelation.</p>"
